Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.68,0:00:05.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Heita\NFor me, girls are like..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.33,0:00:08.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Move over a little, I'm going to sit in here. Kyon~~"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.33,0:00:10.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Right. I understand why girls do that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.82,0:00:13.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,They even do something to their foot and thighs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.34,0:00:15.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,At first, I was like, "what are you doing?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.37,0:00:17.41,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But, deep down inside I'm happy when they do that.\NDo you understand what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.41,0:00:20.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But for me, I fancy girls who jumps lively.\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.33,0:00:22.81,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that girls are prim and proper
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.81,0:00:25.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I fancy girl who shouts "Ah!" and then she falls down flat on the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:27.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And then she will stand up and see her say "Teehee~"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.32,0:00:29.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't understand at all\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.32,0:00:31.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why? Why?\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:33.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you understand at that time that it happened.\NWhy is it that you don't understand right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.33,0:00:35.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Falls flat on the ground?\NYup.\NI don't understand.\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.86,0:00:39.31,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait...\NJust like this feeling. Just like this
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.31,0:00:40.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok ok..yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.82,0:00:45.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I fickle minded?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.32,0:00:49.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I like Kyuto but,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.83,0:00:53.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that there is a woman who is human meant for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.33,0:00:56.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Move over a little\NHere..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.38,0:00:59.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls are kind of scary
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:03.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But, they are cute, moving constantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.82,0:01:06.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,and lively..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.31,0:01:14.31,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.94,0:01:20.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go! Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.84,0:01:24.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Girl playing catchball~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.33,0:01:26.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.82,0:01:33.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yea..just as I thought
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.84,0:01:36.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuto-san that is not how..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.37,0:01:39.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,W...wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.83,0:01:42.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is fun~!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.33,0:01:45.31,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,whoa~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.31,0:01:48.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is fun..\NThis is not fun you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.32,0:01:51.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow~~\NStop!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.32,0:01:55.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you like to do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.37,0:01:57.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.93,0:02:01.81,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Aa! Sorry. Sorry\NI'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.81,0:02:03.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.83,0:02:06.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.34,0:02:13.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does her skin becomes red?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.34,0:02:16.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She's embarrassed. Skin becomes red when you're embarrassed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.34,0:02:19.40,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Her embarrassment shows up to her face
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.40,0:02:21.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuto is embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.83,0:02:24.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You can do it?\NWatch carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.32,0:02:26.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Aa.. Therefore...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.34,0:02:33.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see something like "Nooo~~"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.33,0:02:38.90,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Noooooo..aaaa....uuuuu...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.90,0:02:42.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,u!\NYou're not embarrassed at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.84,0:02:46.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuto is embarrassed! Kyuto is embarrassed!\NStop doing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.34,0:02:48.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying? You startled me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.33,0:02:50.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to give you a break right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:52.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Give me break?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.35,0:02:56.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, please think of me as embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.84,0:02:59.91,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That is embarrassment?\NPuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.91,0:03:02.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I understand.\NFrom now on, you are embarrassed. Jeez
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:08.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That feeling was not a lie
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.85,0:03:13.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,((Between human life and a robot, which is more important?))
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.35,0:03:15.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,((Kyuto))
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.32,0:03:18.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it wasn't a lie but
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.39,0:03:22.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,what is this messed up feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.84,0:03:36.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.. You're embarrassed.\NI get it. So, you can stop doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.35,0:03:44.90,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than being with a girlfriend, this is like accompanying a child
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.90,0:03:48.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Where was the place that I got
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.84,0:03:51.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,this messed up feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:25.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,As the world is singing a song today,\NThere is someone out there who is thinking of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:27.81,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Through songs, you can convey feelings that you can't show
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.81,0:04:31.90,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Today also, just for you, let's sing together "Saraba Koibito" song\N("saraba koibito": Goodbye sweetheart)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:35.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,♪~ I wrote a farewell letter~~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.83,0:04:39.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where are you going?\NAlumni Homecoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.82,0:04:45.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Candies... OK!\NHandkerchief~~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:47.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ticket. Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.36,0:04:58.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,♪~ We were always that happy~~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:05:04.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,♪~ But the two of us was not aware of it~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.85,0:05:07.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,♪~ chachachachachan~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.33,0:05:11.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like you are having so much fun.\NYou think that I am weird right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.84,0:05:13.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You are getting old
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:16.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.\NOk. Ok. I know. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.93,0:05:19.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.33,0:05:23.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to travel forever
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:26.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot pot?\NMy mom went out
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.32,0:05:28.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, it's boring eating alone
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:32.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure\NHuh?! Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.32,0:05:34.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let's go shopping together before going home
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:37.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You even want to do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.33,0:05:42.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,haa~~\NOh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:46.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry\NYou're in a middle of difficult work
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:48.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go back..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:56.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I tighten the rice or the noodle?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:06:02.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been so long since the last time I ate rice at home
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:05.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,For the choir competition, do you have a song in mind that you want to sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.32,0:06:07.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything will do
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.33,0:06:09.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Anything will do" is not what I wanted to hear
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.83,0:06:14.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Something suitable. Something suitable.\N♪～ Both of us were non aware
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.83,0:06:17.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, can you suggest something good?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.35,0:06:21.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I think cod hot pot is better
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:26.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well. What is it? Come on decide quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.33,0:06:28.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, what is the song that you just sang?\N"Taraba Koibito"\N("Taraba": cod)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.85,0:06:31.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Taraba koibito"?\NNo, that's not it..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.33,0:06:33.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell. "Saraba Koibito"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:35.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that good?\NThat one, "taraba"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.32,0:06:38.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, who among you thinks that "taraba koibito" is good?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:40.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Me~\NW...wait. Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.93,0:06:44.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Stop this!\NSensei, are you going to eat cod hot pot today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.83,0:06:46.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'm gonna eat that one
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.32,0:06:55.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:07:00.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We are not in good terms right now
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:03.43,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought she understands
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.43,0:07:05.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawai!?\NShhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.83,0:07:08.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,How am I going to tell her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:14.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hurt her~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:20.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible to tell her now! Absolutely impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:31.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You do understand
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:34.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,that if you are not careful, it will break right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:36.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.34,0:07:43.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Try using this
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.34,0:07:46.91,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold this up to the forehead of Kyuto
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.91,0:07:49.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,and your wish will be granted
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.34,0:07:50.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Pitch
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.33,0:07:55.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!\NThat is disposable
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.82,0:07:57.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.83,0:08:14.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you Runa-chan..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.82,0:08:19.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,aaa! That's good then!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.34,0:08:23.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I will give this to you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.33,0:08:26.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:34.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I see~ You shoplift
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.34,0:08:37.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.34,0:08:42.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not in the position to get mad at you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.33,0:08:47.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I even did something horrible to someone
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.44,0:08:52.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,((If you don't give her to me, I am going to jump from here!))
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.33,0:09:01.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There's always a limit to human's desire
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.82,0:09:06.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I became obvious when I am fixated into something
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.82,0:09:12.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I thought it is ok to become obvious
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.38,0:09:15.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That is..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.83,0:09:18.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,really the worst
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:29.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No one is here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:39.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Im sorry but...can you sit down there for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.37,0:09:53.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:17.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Heita
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.33,0:10:25.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ne~~ Where are we going from now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.82,0:10:28.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I am good to go anywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.82,0:10:31.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,To your favorite place
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:34.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,W...wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.84,0:10:37.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.88,0:10:40.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.82,0:10:43.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Call me Karen
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.35,0:10:45.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,K...Karen-san
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.84,0:10:48.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.84,0:10:51.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,shall we kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:56.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No..I'm ok.\NCome on, let's kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:11:00.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No. No need to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:02.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.35,0:11:15.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.87,0:11:18.42,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is happening here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.42,0:11:20.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuto? Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.34,0:11:22.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Kyuto! Kyuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:26.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She will be fine. Charging is cut off
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.84,0:11:30.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Only half of electric power is used
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.39,0:11:38.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.82,0:11:41.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of person are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:44.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's much better if you don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.33,0:11:47.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be complicated once you know
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.33,0:11:54.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, do not talk about me to any person
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.39,0:11:58.31,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.31,0:12:01.81,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll withdraw Kyuto from you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.82,0:12:08.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,For what reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.34,0:12:13.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuto came here for what reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.34,0:12:16.41,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:19.41,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better if you don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:27.31,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.29,0:12:29.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Store manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:36.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Your elder brother?\NYea
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.79,0:12:39.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,W..why are you here?\NWell..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:41.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a mere acquaintance..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:44.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You embarrassed me!\NI'm not going to forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.88,0:12:48.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never be an adult if you do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.26,0:12:50.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I am very sorry for what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:59.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I can do something
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:01.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:05.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,When I grow up, I will not be poor right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.85,0:13:11.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So that mom and dad will come back home
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.29,0:13:15.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the old days, where all of us go to a family restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.29,0:13:21.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I even ask for a strawberry pancake?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.37,0:13:30.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get mad.\NI'm not angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.80,0:13:39.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's ok. You don't have to force yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.78,0:13:42.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to buy you your pancake!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.27,0:13:50.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.33,0:13:53.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Somebody out there!\NHello!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.76,0:13:56.30,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!\NHello!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.30,0:13:58.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.78,0:14:00.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You can stop that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.79,0:14:05.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If I die like this, nobody will get sad anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.29,0:14:11.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good thing that this happened first
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.86,0:14:13.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.78,0:14:16.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That good thing
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:20.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Up until now, are you happy living with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.79,0:14:28.30,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah~~ the rhythm of kitchen knife is still different
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:30.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,ton ton ton ton...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.35,0:14:32.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That sound is refreshing
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.77,0:14:35.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home~~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:40.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah~~ I'm so tired.\NEh? Aa! Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.28,0:14:43.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really stupid! I mistook a wrong date!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.28,0:14:46.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Well...Don't say that. Try checking again one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:49.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? We're going to eat hot pot today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.33,0:14:52.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you make this?\NI'm not the one making..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.77,0:14:59.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for interrupting~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.78,0:15:05.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,W...wait\NWhere are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.27,0:15:08.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.29,0:15:12.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.\NLet's eat. Let's eat
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.86,0:15:16.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let her go like that!\NEh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.28,0:15:18.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.28,0:15:24.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,♪~ Both of us is not aware
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.29,0:15:27.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,♪~ chachachachachan
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.83,0:15:39.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw that. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.77,0:15:44.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take good care of my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:48.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I am not good for him..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.29,0:15:49.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:53.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well.. However I think of it, I am not worth it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.78,0:15:57.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought, my son won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.82,0:16:01.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I also think of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:05.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...that's not what I mean..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.26,0:16:12.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I am only thinking of myself as how am I going to live
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:14.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,For the two of us..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.77,0:16:17.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not capable of giving
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.32,0:16:21.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,a decent home, properly.\NProperly?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.76,0:16:27.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ogawa-sensei is like a crushed shop that is now growing..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:31.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,able to sacrifice something of his own...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.27,0:16:33.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I am unable to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.29,0:16:37.81,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the same.\NThat's because it's who you are
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:39.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Up until now, have you heard of a place
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.86,0:16:44.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,where someone was able to sacrifice a lot of things?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:47.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the same
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:51.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Choose something that you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.29,0:16:56.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that, in the end, you can say "because I am here"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.32,0:17:01.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:08.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool wind is blowing~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.27,0:17:13.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to a town alone at dawn~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.28,0:17:17.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the bad guy~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.78,0:17:22.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You are not the one~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.87,0:17:27.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Shaking from the window of the train~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.78,0:17:32.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, houses became so small~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.26,0:17:37.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Without knowing, I cried heavily in my heart~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.29,0:17:42.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be back for sure~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:51.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We were always that happy~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.28,0:17:58.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But both of us were not aware of it~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.79,0:18:01.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,chachachachachan~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.28,0:18:05.81,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a map that guides me how to go back home~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:10.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll probably throw it into the sea of tears~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.79,0:18:15.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the bad guy here~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.29,0:18:18.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You are not the one~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.29,0:18:33.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.\NEh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:34.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:43.30,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.28,0:18:54.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That song awhile ago, is just a random song that we're going to sing right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.78,0:18:57.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we're eventually following it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.77,0:19:02.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so happy that I was unaware of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.29,0:19:04.81,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I think so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.81,0:19:09.81,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And that part, "I am the bad guy, You are not the one"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.78,0:19:14.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujioka-kun thinks like an adult
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.77,0:19:21.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Nakao-kun and Fujioka-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.29,0:19:24.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I really want to watch something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.29,0:19:27.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?\NYou want to watch something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:31.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's boring right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.28,0:19:33.80,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:37.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh..you're going back home?\NYup. I'll go home
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.27,0:19:39.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,≪ Tatsuya wait! ≫\NKya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.78,0:19:46.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch~ That hurts~~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.27,0:19:52.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you in pain or something?\NEh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.27,0:19:57.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...I'm okay. I'm ok.\NBut...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.29,0:20:01.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! It's now time for my IV
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.78,0:20:04.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But you have IV right now\NEh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.78,0:20:08.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Y..yeah you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:10.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ano...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:14.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.26,0:20:17.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kubo-kun, sorry for the wait~~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:23.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.79,0:20:26.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No..nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.78,0:20:38.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like something is wrong with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.79,0:20:42.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.77,0:20:45.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I am afraid to die
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.77,0:20:48.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really scared of death
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.78,0:20:51.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Weird right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.83,0:20:54.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm weird
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:20:59.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not weird
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.27,0:21:04.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too. I always think what will happen to me tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.29,0:21:10.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been thinking of that up until now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.80,0:21:16.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, I'll go out with Kubo-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.37,0:21:18.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...that's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.77,0:21:22.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what is it? I don't understand what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.28,0:21:26.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry sorry. What I mean is..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.78,0:21:29.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him that he must live longer.\NHa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.78,0:21:34.31,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since Kubo met you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:37.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been saying "I'm afraid to die"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.38,0:21:42.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Although he says "I'm scared" I know he doesn't really mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.76,0:21:45.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But then, why "I'm afraid to die" all of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.77,0:21:51.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamamoto is scared of dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.29,0:21:54.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, I can't imagine it..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.78,0:21:59.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.85,0:22:04.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,the most important person to you is suddenly gone..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.29,0:22:06.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno what am I going to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.79,0:22:11.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, I want to tell him not to say something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.78,0:22:18.30,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Just live longer each day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.30,0:22:21.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.30,0:22:38.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,((Shall we kiss?))
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.27,0:22:40.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,♪~ ((chachachachachan))
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.78,0:22:52.80,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.80,0:22:55.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you from Kyuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.29,0:22:58.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a memory about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.29,0:23:02.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you? Where do you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.28,0:23:04.80,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.80,0:23:08.80,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember also.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.79,0:23:17.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.28,0:23:22.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know anything much about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.34,0:23:31.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.71,0:23:52.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.71,0:23:57.74,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.74,0:24:02.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I'm getting used to liking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.21,0:24:05.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the texture. It feels good when touching it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.71,0:24:11.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking of starting to work during daytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.20,0:24:13.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.68,0:24:19.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So does that mean, you're not coming to school anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.27,0:24:21.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.21,0:24:25.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.70,0:24:31.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the principal here. Yet I can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.30,0:24:45.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,♪~ Cool wind blowing
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.70,0:24:50.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,♪~ Going to a town alone at dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.72,0:24:55.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,♪~ I'm the bad guy here
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.21,0:24:58.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,♪~ You're not the one
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.73,0:25:03.80,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujioka-kun has quit school
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.80,0:25:06.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean quit?\NSo, he's not coming anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.19,0:25:08.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that?\NWell, we don't
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.72,0:25:10.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,know his reasons right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.69,0:25:13.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.21,0:25:15.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly quitting without saying anything to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.71,0:25:18.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But that is something that can't be helped, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.20,0:25:20.75,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably because of family matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.75,0:25:23.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But, can't we do something about it?\NYou're right
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.29,0:25:26.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't receive his diploma
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.71,0:25:30.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this normally happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.19,0:25:32.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.71,0:25:36.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakao-kun, do you know something?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.20,0:25:38.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.72,0:25:40.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Why Nakao-kun knows something?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.72,0:25:44.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a video site where Nakao-kun and Fujioka-kun appeared
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.29,0:25:46.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You were inside the elevator that stuck, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.69,0:25:48.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.71,0:25:51.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean the elevator stuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.20,0:25:54.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?\NWhat happened inside the elevator?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.72,0:26:02.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,F...Fujioka's younger brother shoplifted...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.24,0:26:08.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujioka got mad to his younger brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.22,0:26:12.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,((When I grow up, I will not be poor right?))
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.70,0:26:18.74,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujioka said "I'm going to buy you your pancake"...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.74,0:26:23.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So, we went to a restaurant and rode the elevator..
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.22,0:26:31.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Hey! Hey!\NHello! Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.22,0:26:34.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough already
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.26,0:26:36.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You can stop now
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.79,0:26:40.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good thing that this has happened
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.21,0:26:42.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.20,0:26:45.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That one. It's good thing
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.70,0:26:53.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Up until now, are you happy that you're living with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.22,0:27:01.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I am
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.22,0:27:03.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the day you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.26,0:27:12.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.71,0:27:15.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,it snowed
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.70,0:27:20.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a call from dad..
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.20,0:27:23.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,He said "you have a younger brother that is born"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.71,0:27:26.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking..
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.20,0:27:35.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,when you grow up, we can play snowball fight together
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.70,0:27:49.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say enough already
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.22,0:27:56.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have to play snowball fight together!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.21,0:28:20.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,When we get out of here...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.27,0:28:27.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have a lot things to do together
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.20,0:28:38.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible that we can do everything right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.20,0:28:44.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's continue the practice and then let's go home
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.69,0:28:47.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let's try again memorizing "Saraba Koibito" in our heads
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.26,0:28:51.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell Fujioka...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.70,0:28:57.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,As the world is singing a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.20,0:29:00.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody is thinking of you somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.20,0:29:02.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Through songs, you can convey feelings that we can't show
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.69,0:29:07.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's sing together for the sake of Fujioka!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.71,0:29:10.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of Fujioka?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.76,0:29:14.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,To deliver our innermost feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.70,0:29:16.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,How are we going to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.70,0:29:20.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What about we sing in front of Fujioka-kun's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.22,0:29:23.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I think somebody will get angry.\NI don't want to be caught by the police
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.69,0:29:26.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's probably right.\NBut..
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.70,0:29:28.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.80,0:29:37.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen if the heart of everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.19,0:29:39.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,is not properly conveyed?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.20,0:29:52.74,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it really that we wanted to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.74,0:29:55.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it "Goodbye. Where are you going?"
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.13,0:30:14.13,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.17,0:30:17.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your fortune. This is my fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.72,0:30:20.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.66,0:30:25.64,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably think that I'm stubborn
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.64,0:30:27.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.65,0:30:30.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I will definitely survive
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.65,0:30:34.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, suddenly appearing in front of you. I'll never go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.15,0:30:37.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.22,0:30:39.14,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just saying
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.15,0:30:55.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayato, go take a bath\NOk
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.15,0:31:40.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,♪~ ≪I wrote a goodbye letter≫
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.17,0:31:43.64,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,♪~ ≪I placed it on the table≫
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.64,0:31:45.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Onichan!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.17,0:31:49.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,♪~ ≪I see your sleeping face≫
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.24,0:31:53.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,♪~ ≪I went out quietly≫
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.66,0:32:02.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,♪~ We are always happy
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.16,0:32:08.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,♪~ But the two of us were non aware
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.70,0:32:10.73,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,♪~ chachachachachan
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.73,0:32:15.14,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,♪~ The cool air is blowing
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.14,0:32:19.64,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,♪~ And I'm going to town alone at dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.64,0:32:23.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,♪~ I'm the bad guy here
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.66,0:32:28.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,♪~ You are not the one
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.17,0:32:31.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,♪~ shaking from the window train
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.70,0:32:34.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!\NI'm going to call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.26,0:32:37.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,They are singing loudly outside someone's house\NIt's troublesome
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.16,0:32:41.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,♪~ I cried heavily in my chest
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.15,0:32:45.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,♪~ I'll come back for sure
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.65,0:32:54.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,♪~ We are always that happy
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.24,0:33:01.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,♪~ But the two of us were non aware
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.16,0:33:14.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really very sorry.\NBe careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.16,0:33:17.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them do such things again..
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.22,0:33:20.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Guide them properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.64,0:33:28.64,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone gathered around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.64,0:33:32.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it that all of you are depressed?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.66,0:33:35.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.15,0:33:37.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There are certain things that we can't convey
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.67,0:33:40.74,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? You were glad that you were able to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.74,0:33:43.64,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm glad that I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.64,0:33:46.14,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujioka looked happy though
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.14,0:33:49.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But, when I saw sensei apologizing to the cops..
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.65,0:33:52.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's ok. It doesn't matter how many times I bow down my head
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.65,0:33:55.14,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It is my job to bow down my head anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.14,0:33:59.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I was used to be called as "Kishimoto pecker"
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.19,0:34:01.23,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, drink it!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.23,0:34:03.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's drink quietly. Let's drink quietly though~
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.66,0:34:07.13,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,In cue, you will drink it
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.13,0:34:10.13,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.13,0:34:14.13,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.64,0:34:19.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,≪Thank you ≫\NThis time, it's goodbye~
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.71,0:34:21.75,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,≪ goodbye ≫
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.75,0:34:24.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujioka-kun is strong willed right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.67,0:34:30.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,As compared to me, I don't have the guts to do that
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.15,0:34:33.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not the only one thinking like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.71,0:34:42.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we break-up?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.64,0:34:53.14,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I have always known it before
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.16,0:35:01.14,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The best way for us is ...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.14,0:35:04.14,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,saying goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.64,0:35:11.14,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you been thinking right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.15,0:35:24.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to properly see the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.18,0:35:27.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This what you call, painful reality
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.17,0:35:37.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is like drama right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.66,0:35:44.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the drama, I'm going to say it properly...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.20,0:35:48.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.14,0:35:57.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.16,0:35:59.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.16,0:36:01.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You came back at a wrong timing
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.65,0:36:04.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?\NOh! You came back
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.15,0:36:07.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.\NI'm going to start in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.65,0:36:09.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here.\NWhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.66,0:36:20.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.65,0:36:22.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Japanese dance.\NHah?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.65,0:36:25.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that next Sunday, there is a concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.65,0:36:27.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Rehearsal
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.16,0:36:31.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...This something that a family member should not see
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.66,0:36:36.25,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She's stubborn\NJust bear with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.64,0:36:48.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,sigh~\NThat hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.66,0:36:53.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is she aiming for?\NWe have no choice..
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.16,0:36:55.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she wants do it since she was young.\NSo, I just have to bear with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.65,0:36:58.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She just randomly wanted to do what the adolescents are doing nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.69,0:37:01.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, mom cried a long time ago right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.24,0:37:02.64,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.64,0:37:05.64,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,((Don't! Don't cry! Don't do it!))
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.64,0:37:08.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,((It's not good doing that!))
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.16,0:37:09.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,((You will be ok))
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.66,0:37:14.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I was really angry that time. And I said to myself I'll surely go to the toilet
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.72,0:37:17.64,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I will definitely cry inside
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.64,0:37:20.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to take back the minutes that you cried
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.16,0:37:23.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Just accompany me ok?\NOk? ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.15,0:37:27.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Part 2 will now begin
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.15,0:37:28.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.65,0:37:30.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!\NThere's a part 2?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.67,0:37:33.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know! I really don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.23,0:38:04.73,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need anything that is coming from you
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.15,0:38:10.14,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't overdo it
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.14,0:38:13.14,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's not about overdoing it
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.17,0:38:21.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, do you know everything about Kyuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.15,0:38:23.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.20,0:38:25.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Even her embarrassed face?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.16,0:38:30.64,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Q10 is built within an artificial muscle
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.64,0:38:33.64,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Regarding her complicated facial expression, I can't answer you that
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.14,0:38:42.14,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuto has an embarrassed face
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.14,0:38:50.14,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why, I'm telling you she isn't your belonging
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.65,0:38:56.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Q10 ...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.65,0:38:59.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,belongs to us
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.14,0:39:16.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.65,0:39:40.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuto
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.22,0:39:47.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a rainbow!\NA beautiful rainbow appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.66,0:39:52.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's look at it together
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.15,0:40:02.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something you wanted to say to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.65,0:40:06.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Well, even if I say something...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.26,0:40:14.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Aa...I hope that...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.65,0:40:18.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuto will not cry in the future
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.15,0:40:21.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Puff
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.16,0:40:23.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Please turn your head to the other side
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.65,0:40:37.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.14,0:40:42.64,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.66,0:40:45.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,These are my tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.65,0:40:47.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,These are tears?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.65,0:40:50.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on,I'm not going to cry anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.68,0:40:53.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll not cry forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.24,0:40:56.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.66,0:41:01.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...I wonder what robot's life is...\N250 years later
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.66,0:41:04.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll not cry? For 250 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.15,0:41:06.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do if you cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.72,0:41:10.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just remember Heita
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.64,0:41:14.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I remember Heita,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.16,0:41:16.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I will smile instead
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.65,0:41:27.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.72,0:41:34.14,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm embarrassed when you say that
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.14,0:41:38.64,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me see an embarrassed face
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.16,0:41:48.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuto is embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.63,0:42:16.63,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think the sky is also embarrassed?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.66,0:42:21.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Puff
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.64,0:42:27.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,After the tears are drawn out,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.16,0:42:29.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I somehow feel that Kyuto was
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.65,0:42:33.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,able to fill up the emptiness inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.69,0:42:38.14,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,These tears as the evidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.14,0:42:41.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,that I'll see 250 years later...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.65,0:42:46.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuto is still able to live though
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.15,0:42:51.64,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to enter a cave that is less crowded...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.64,0:42:54.64,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,not completely filled up as time passes by
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.64,0:43:01.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But, she is
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.15,0:43:03.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,a proof that there is an important person
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.14,0:43:09.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Tomorrow I'll do my best for mankind!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.16,0:43:14.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a proof that we have to continue living for that special someone
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.15,0:43:20.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'm satisfied with everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.65,0:43:23.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like in childhood...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.65,0:43:27.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I'll able to go back before...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.66,0:43:33.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine the way I am
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.70,0:43:36.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You poor thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.64,0:43:42.14,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.69,0:43:59.14,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I have met Kyuto
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.14,0:44:01.64,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That is all that matters
